{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"111f8973ef","title":"中央关于三万人口以上城市召开各界代表会议的规定","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"695150c2ff","index":0,"year":1949,"month":8,"day":19,"articleId":"111f8973ef"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"264f5dfcbe","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的给各中央局和分局的电报。"}],"contents":[{"id":"525ca773df","type":"title","text":"中央关于三万人口以上城市召开各界代表会议的规定“","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef"},{"id":"264f5dfcbe","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局、分局：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef"},{"id":"631b1d6609","type":"paragraph","text":"太原解放至今不到三个月，开了五次各界代表会议，成绩极好。各地除石家庄、上海、北平已报告开会外尚未据报开会，这是很不好的。兹规定","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef"},{"id":"4139c68f5f","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）三万以上人口城市均须开各界代表会。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef"},{"id":"ba4eb83c6d","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）会期：中小城市至少每月一次，每次一天，至多两天。大城市每月或每两月一次，每次一天两天，至多三天。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef"},{"id":"87f0221aff","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）每次解决问题不要多，应集中在一两个问题上","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef"},{"id":"bf4594b15b","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）代表应固定为半年改选一次，连选者得连任。在六个月内，不称职者临时改换，未吸收者逐步增加。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef"},{"id":"61b959262f","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）代表会毕，有向人民传达和解释会议报告和决定的任务。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef"},{"id":"0f9c771efb","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）此指示转达所属三方人口以上的一切城市勿误","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef"},{"id":"44527fb758","type":"paragraph","text":"（七）你们应重视此事，总结经验，报告中央为要","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef"},{"id":"fc0d0a273f","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef"},{"id":"e5ae53a57f","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十九日","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef"}],"page":{"id":"1e2e818fda","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"111f8973ef","start":154,"end":154}}}},"__N_SSG":true}